N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 369.5 - Hours for public inspection and copying

State Regulations

The division shall accept requests for records and produce
records during regular business hours, which are 9:00 a.m. to 5:00
p.m. Notes
